vola, P., Pieterse, A., Wastewater purification efficiency in experimental treatment wetlands in Estonia (2001) Nutrient Transformations in Natural and Constructed Wetlands, pp. 201-224. , J. Vymazal (ed.), Backhuys Publishers, Leiden; Martikainen, P.J., Nykänen, H., Crill, P., Silvola, J., Effect of a lowered water table on nitrous oxide fluxes from northern peatlands (1993) Nature, 366, pp. 51-53; Mosier, A.R., Soil processes and global changes (1998) Biol. Fertil. Soils, 27, pp. 221-229; Scholefield, D., Hawkins, J.M.B., Jackson, S.M., Development of a helium atmosphere soil incubation technique for direct measurement of nitrous oxide and dinitrogen fluxes during denitrification (1997) Soil Biol. Biochem., 29 (9-10), pp. 1345-1352; Tai, P.-D., Li, P.-D., Sun, T.-H., He, Y.-W., Zhou, Q.-Z., Gong, Z.-Q., Mizuochi, M., Inamori, Y., Greenhouse gas emissions from a constructed wetland for municipal sewage treatment (2002) Journal of Environmental Sciences (China), 14 (1), pp. 27-33; Tanner, C.C., Adams, D.D., Downes, M.T., Methane emissions from constructed wetlands treating agricultural wastewaters (1997) J. Environ. Qual., 26 (4), pp. 1056-1062; Tanner, C.C., Kadlec, R.H., Gibbs, M.M., Sukias, J.P.S., Nguyen, M.L., Nitrogen processing gradients in subsurface-flow wetlands - Influence of wastewater characteristics (2002) Ecol. Eng., 18, pp. 499-520; Watts, S., Seitzinger, S.P., Denitrification rates in organic and mineral soils from riparian sites: A comparison of N2 flux and acetylene inhibition methods (2000) Soil Biol. Biochem., 32, pp. 1383-1392; Wild, U., Lenz, A., Kamp, T., Heinz, S., Pfadenhauer, J., Vegetation development, nutrient removal and trace gas fluxes in constructed Typha wetlands (2002) Advances in Ecological Sciences 12, pp. 101-125. , WIT Press, Southampton, Boston","Mander, Ü.; Institute of Geography, University of Tartu, 46 Vanemuise St., 51014 Tartu, Estonia; email: mander@ut.ee",,,,,,,,02731223,,WSTED,14621157,"English","Water Sci. Technol.",C